%^BOLD%^-=%^CYAN%^Undeath Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The undeath domain deals with all things unliving.

Clerics with the Undeath Domain are healed, rather than harmed, by negative energy.

This domain also grants %^RED%^BOLD%^Bleeding Touch%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The undeath domain contains the following spells:

Repair Undead, Command Undead, Necrophage, Animate Dead, Mass Repair Undead, Create Undead, Control Undead, Create Greater Undead, Animus Blizzard

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nilith

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^